item.title: Un ip ban
item.dc:creator: @kingofnone kingofnone
item.description:
@kingofnone wrote:

ok dude
this has to be the easiest thing to do so it wont be hard…

first off go to your charecter folder
now look for the guy who got iped and copy his ip (you will need to be able to paste this in a sec)

go to your data folder… after that go to your bannedip’s file and double click it search for the ip that was banned and highlight it and hit backspace and save

wala hes unbanned
